Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:35.59,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,2000)}The Fearsome Ability of the Shadow Fruit!\NThe Ultimate Number 900!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:38.18,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,It's not over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:40.07,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Despite cutting him, he's still a zombie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.07,0:02:41.43,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,He'll keep getting up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:44.58,Main,Spider,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:49.08,Main,Spider,0,0,0,,Wait a sec... I've seen you before...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:52.50,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Worry not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:54.30,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I've finished him off already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:55.67,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:58.90,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,These zombies have a weak point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:08.12,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:11.04,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,That's the zombie's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:13.16,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:14.71,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,It's coming out right before our eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:19.07,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Now, return to your master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:32.00,Main,Mouse,0,0,0,,Commander Tararan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:35.23,Main,Mouse,0,0,0,,The commander was defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.57,0:03:37.48,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,He completely stopped moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:38.78,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,What did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:40.04,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Purification.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:40.92,Main,Mouse,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:43.80,Main,Mouse,0,0,0,,There's no doubt, he is the "Humming One".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:48.10,Main,Mouse,0,0,0,,He's the man who caused a ruckus in Thriller Bark five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:50.35,Main,Mouse,0,0,0,,Inform master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:57.84,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,This spider's web is indeed strong against physical force, but still weak to fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:03.02,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:03.93,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,It melted!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.37,0:04:06.64,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Straw Hat and the others were abducted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:09.75,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,It seems you know quite a lot about this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:10.50,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:13.84,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,However, I'm not quite sure how to put this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:18.90,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,The fact that they've been captured means there is a strong possibility it may already be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:20.97,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:22.36,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Too late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:25.26,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,P-Please don't get mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:27.03,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Let's keep a straight face!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:30.10,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Even though as a skeleton, I don't have a face!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:34.13,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Skull joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.74,0:04:38.13,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Stop it, he's already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:40.00,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:43.13,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Stop joking and listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:45.68,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Stop it, he's already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:49.88,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,It is as I told you on the ship, when my ship's rudder failed,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:53.93,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I began wandering the sea alone decades ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:05:01.61,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I thought of escaping this evil sea, but with the rudder broken I was just a puppet of the sea current.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:05.23,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,That was more than five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.23,0:05:10.83,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,And just like you now, I eventually was lead to Thriller Bark.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:15.46,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I wanted to leave the Florian Triangle no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:21.19,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Hoping that there might be parts to fix the rudder on the island, I investigated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:30.05,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,When I entered, I found nothing but zombies and monsters in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:34.02,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Before long I was captured and brought to this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:45.44,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Inside I saw a combat dancer who was caught earlier and a patched corpse which they called a marionette.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:49.43,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Afterwards, a terrifying and huge man appeared, and...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:53.49,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,He tore the man's shadow from the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:55.29,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,He cut it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:56.91,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,His shadow was cut off?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:06:00.38,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I thought my eyes were deceiving me... even though...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:02.23,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I don't have any eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:07.73,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Stop joking or I'll kick your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:09.18,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,I don't mind if you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:19.48,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I was to have the same fate before long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:22.61,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,The one whose shadow was taken collapsed where he stood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.41,0:06:27.31,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,On the other hand, his severed shadow was pressed inside the unmoving body of the marionette.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:29.21,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I didn't think that was possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.21,0:06:31.62,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,How he did it, I'm unsure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:34.06,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,But, the marionette corpse just...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:37.25,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Started moving on its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:39.42,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:45.80,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,A shadow is another soul that goes and moves along with you anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:48.76,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,It follows you from birth to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:55.20,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,It's a soul that will never leave you, that will always obey and follow you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:07:00.23,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,The man that seizes these, and has them obey his will is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:03.55,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,The Royal Warlord of the Sea, Gekko Moriah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:07.65,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,The user of the Shadow Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:09.36,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,A devil fruit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:15.64,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,As long as there's a corpse, he can use a shadow to bring forth a zombie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:24.54,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,The problem is that the genius surgeon who creates these tough creatures, Doctor Hogback... has friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:29.19,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,In some cases, he gets parts from different graveyards...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:32.26,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Using the corpses of legendary warriors to revive them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:39.18,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Moreover, he has an immense amount of enumerated marionettes still stored in a freezer in his lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:41.79,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Dr. Hogback...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:48.80,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,So that famous doctor came to this place after the incident of his disappearance to help a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:55.49,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Then, the zombies' bodies can move, so it's not like they've been resurrected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:58.13,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.13,0:08:02.64,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,The shadow holds both the personality and fighting skills of its owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:06.90,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,The physical strength of the marionette is limited by the power of it's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:12.27,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,When both strong shadow and body are merged, the result is an even more powerful zombie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:18.59,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,That is why Moriah so eagerly desires the shadows of bounty heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.59,0:08:19.93,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:22.43,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,They were after us from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:24.69,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,So that's the whole story of Thriller Bark.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:29.82,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,To Moriah, the zombie's most important characteristic might be obedience.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:33.57,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,The stronger the warrior the harder it must be to make it listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:37.53,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,True... they receive the same fighting spirit and skill as their owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:42.25,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,The strong ones are set adrift at sea after they lose consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:44.21,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Then, they...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:46.17,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:47.47,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,They're safe yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:48.68,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,We have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:51.96,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Right now I will tell you the best plan we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:55.11,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,So please, trust me and do as I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.74,0:08:57.76,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Trust you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:02.47,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Skull Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:08.56,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I haven't had a conversation like this in decades! It's so fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:10.98,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,We're listening, so tell us quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:11.92,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:15.30,Main,Zombies,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:17.61,Main,Zombies,0,0,0,,The Three Mysterious Persons have arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:20.58,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,That was quick. Enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:22.83,Main,Zombies,0,0,0,,Please, come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:31.92,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,You finally came.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:37.43,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Make me the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:39.02,Main,All,0,0,0,,Very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:41.12,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,You're no Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:45.60,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,The Pirate King will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:47.64,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:50.77,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey! Untie this string you giant leek!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:54.68,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Usopp, Nami, Chopper, Sanji, Zoro... Give them all back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:57.01,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Where did you take them, leek?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:59.66,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,What a splendidly strong man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:01.89,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,So this is Straw Hat Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:04.33,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Hey, Straw Hat Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:06.29,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,You mentioned many names.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:09.21,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,We've only captured three of you so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:16.21,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,The Pirate Hunter Zoro and a blond guy with no wanted poster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.46,0:10:19.76,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Could that blond guy be Sanji...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:23.30,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:26.08,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Hey, it seems Zoro and Sanji also got caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:29.33,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,No way, and Luffy was also caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:34.12,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,H-How come that monstrous trio got caught so easily?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:40.03,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,I don't know who these guys are, but they're definitely bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:45.24,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,By the way, what happened with those three, Perona?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:48.29,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,The Risky Brothers were supposed to deliver them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:51.31,Main,Perona,0,0,0,,They didn't bring them to Kumashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:53.92,Main,Perona,0,0,0,,Didn't they escape while they were being delivered?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:57.74,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,They're talking about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:01.51,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Don't say it. You... Don't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:03.95,Main,Perona,0,0,0,,I told you not to open your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:06.37,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,You're too strict with Kumashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.37,0:11:07.56,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Way too strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:11.63,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Anyways, I was trying to get a hold of my bride when those three...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:15.11,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Ran into your garden and caused a disturbance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.89,0:11:17.69,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:20.20,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,That means... Hogback...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:24.51,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Bastard, do you mean that one of you laid a hand on my bride?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.80,0:11:27.28,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,So that's what happened before!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:29.76,Main,Cindry,0,0,0,,Your bride is not coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.76,0:11:31.84,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,What was that, Cindry!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:36.28,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey! Cindry-chan, you're making it worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:39.38,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,And why did you step out in front of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:41.45,Main,Cindry,0,0,0,,Yours won't be coming either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:44.85,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,What a low blow! Where did that come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:46.81,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:48.93,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Stop this pointless discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:52.73,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,If some pirates got away, then you guys can do something about it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:12:01.07,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,I gathered you here to celebrate the creation of a great fighting asset.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:08.17,Main,Zombies,0,0,0,,Who is that guy!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:11.39,Main,Zombies,0,0,0,,Master, that pirate bit the cage apart to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:12.85,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,He...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:15.51,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Bit the cage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:18.84,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,What're you gonna do to catch me now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:23.18,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,What a promising man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.65,0:12:27.22,Main,Perona,0,0,0,,Wait, Absalom, we're inside a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:28.50,Main,Perona,0,0,0,,I'll stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.67,0:12:31.58,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Like you'd catch me, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:33.71,Main,Perona,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Negative Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:47.57,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,If I were to be reborn, I want to become a sea slug...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:52.43,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,The man who just said he wanted to be Pirate King now wants to be a sea slug...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:53.58,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Atrocious...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:55.79,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Turn the light on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:12:58.53,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,What're you doing, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:13:00.73,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,You'll regret this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:12.22,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,W-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:13.55,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,My shadow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:27.77,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,I finally have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:29.83,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,The 300 million fighting power!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:34.60,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,With this, the Ultimate Special Zombie can be created!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:42.59,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Go back to the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:44.87,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,To the Sunny?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:46.47,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:53.49,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,The worst case scenario is that your friends have been captured and their shadows have been stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:57.64,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,However, having their shadow stolen isn't going to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:14:00.63,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Take a look at what happened to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.63,0:14:02.46,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Ah, I died!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:04.05,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,That's a different story!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:06.07,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:10.26,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,In short, even if they got their shadow stolen, they won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:11.71,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:15.56,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,However, the moment their shadows are taken, they become vulnerable as they lose consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:17.58,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,And won't wake up for two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:23.46,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,During this time they put those who are strong into boats and cast them off from Thriller Bark.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:27.05,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I've said this before but, do you know why they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:31.61,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,So that the victims won't attempt to return to the island and reclaim their shadows, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.61,0:14:32.71,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:35.71,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Then, why not just kill them while they're unconscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.71,0:14:37.66,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,They cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:41.21,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,This is very important, so listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:44.55,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,First of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:48.48,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Although the body and the shadow may be separated, they're part of one being.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:51.68,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,If the body dies, then the shadow is doomed as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:56.01,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,In other words, the moment that happens, the zombie will also perish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.01,0:15:00.48,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,This means trouble for the enemy, so they make sure to keep the body alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:05.71,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Which means that, even if your friends have been stripped off their shadows...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:09.64,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,They are surely alive and are being taken back to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:13.30,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,That's why...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:18.77,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,If you two become victims as well, this will turn into the worst case scenario!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:23.65,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Everyone would've lost their shadows and will be left to wander the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:28.92,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,But something can still be done. If we wake up your friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:33.42,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,We'll have one chance to figure out how to recover the stolen shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.67,0:15:37.37,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Did you get all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.42,0:15:40.18,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:42.84,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:44.13,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Take this, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:45.16,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:48.55,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,The zombies' weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:53.01,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,It's effectiveness against the Spider Monkey is proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:54.38,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Weakness?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.38,0:15:55.82,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:15:58.81,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:00.58,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Salt?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:04.92,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,So it's kinda like we're defeating some evil being by purifying it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:07.45,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Well, you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:11.51,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,The zombies are originally animated by the power of the devil fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:14.94,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Just as the sea nullifies the abilities of a devil fruit user...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.94,0:16:21.87,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,the salt which has the sea's power undoes the bond between the false soul and the corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:23.51,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:29.94,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,So that thing that flew out of the monkey's mouth a little while ago was the shadow from within his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:32.11,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,To think they had such a weakness...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.11,0:16:37.00,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Now then, to defeat the Zombies, simply throw the salt into their mouths!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:38.31,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,That's the trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:39.77,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,The only trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:40.86,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,The trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:42.74,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,The trick, the trick, the trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.07,0:16:42.25,Secondary,Robin,0,0,0,,But Brook...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.74,0:16:47.12,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Why is it that you happen to know so much about this island and the zombies?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.12,0:16:50.32,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,When my shadow was stolen five years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:57.95,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Naturally, I was cast off in my ship, but luckily enough I woke up in time to find a way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:02.64,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,And then I returned to the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:03.91,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,To fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:10.92,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,The zombie that has my shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:17.11,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,But... I was completely defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:23.37,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I shamefully ran to save my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:25.37,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,No matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:28.50,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,No matter what... I didn't want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:33.44,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Because I was the sole survivor from my ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:41.41,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Because I promised my friends that one day I'd escape from this Devil Sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:43.87,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I shamefully ran to save my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:51.96,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,And though I managed to live a long while, I was unable to achieve any resolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:55.47,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,That's why... I will not escape this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:58.05,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Until I beat that man and recover my shadow I-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:05.03,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:09.32,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Please excuse me, I'll go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:10.05,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Have a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.05,0:18:11.77,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:19.03,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,While we're still at it, just answer me one more question.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:28.13,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,L-Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:32.36,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,What was that... just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:34.29,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,His shadow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.29,0:18:35.94,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,His shadow was ripped off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.87,0:18:41.26,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,It's just like the story that skeleton Brook told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:46.02,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,If his shadow was taken... then that means this guy also took Brook's!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:47.49,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I can't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.49,0:18:50.12,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,How come he can do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:54.83,Main,Perona,0,0,0,,Kumashi! You were blabbering again weren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.83,0:18:57.67,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,You're too strict with Kumashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.67,0:18:58.86,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Way too strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.14,0:19:07.08,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,This guy will bring me one step closer to being the Pirate King, right Hogback?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.28,0:19:16.27,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Since the day I met you ten years ago, I've served you for the day Number 900 would be made.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.27,0:19:19.94,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,With that shadow we can create the greatest zombie ever made...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:23.45,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,And without a doubt, it'll become a huge source of power for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:29.85,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,The day that I will be known worldwide as the Graveyard King has come closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:38.40,Main,Perona,0,0,0,,My dream kingdom where all the world's cute things will become zombies and serve me is before my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.89,0:19:44.10,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Even the most insolent bastard will become an obedient zombie if I take his shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:48.41,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,I'll turn this world into one full of obedient zombies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:50.64,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,If I had a servant like this back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:56.04,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have lost to that idiot Kaidou in the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:59.21,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Let's wake him up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:00.23,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Gyoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:00.86,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Nin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.86,0:20:01.57,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Bao!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:03.32,Main,Zombies,0,0,0,,Yes, master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:06.38,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Open the door to the special freezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:08.24,Main,Zombies,0,0,0,,Right away, master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.13,0:20:14.35,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Just you wait, 900.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:17.28,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Spider Mouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:21.72,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Dump Straw Hat Luffy's body on his ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:25.41,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,And don't forget to remove the thread, it'll be troublesome if he dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:26.53,Main,Mouse,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:28.37,Main,Mouse,0,0,0,,Please wait! I have a report!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:29.86,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:34.83,Main,Mouse,0,0,0,,Just now, Commander Spider Monkey Tararan was defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:37.43,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:40.26,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,That's not possible, unless his shadow is extracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:42.33,Main,Mouse,0,0,0,,His shadow was extracted!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:47.20,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Absalom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:50.61,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,The only man capable of such a thing, is him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.61,0:20:53.52,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,The Chivalrous Humming Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:56.97,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,It seems the report Hildon gave me wasn't wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.97,0:20:58.02,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:21:00.90,Main,Mouse,0,0,0,,The Humming One has been freeing lots of shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:04.05,Main,Mouse,0,0,0,,Before I knew it, there were countless victims!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:08.87,Main,Mouse,0,0,0,,At this rate, the nightmare from five years ago will be repeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.69,0:21:14.85,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Damn... He's the only man who could tell the zombies' weakn-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.85,0:21:16.02,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:17.63,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,How did he find out-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:21.00,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Cindry-chan, why're you standing in front of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:25.76,Main,Perona,0,0,0,,I've heard about him but... what is he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:30.73,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Perona, you don't know what he looks like?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:34.18,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Then, that's why he wasn't spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:35.52,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:37.66,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,That troublemaker has come once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.66,0:21:41.12,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Like I care about such a thing, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.12,0:21:43.65,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,You take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.76,0:21:43.65,Secondary,Absalom,0,0,0,,H-Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.65,0:21:47.70,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Now, on to the freezer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.74,0:21:55.28,Main,Mouse,0,0,0,,Still, the current situation is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.22,0:22:00.03,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Idiot! Say that in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.03,0:22:02.52,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,In that case, we should be able to contain him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.52,0:22:03.17,Main,Mouse,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:06.20,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,If there's a problem when he wakes up, report it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.20,0:22:07.88,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Now go ahead and throw Straw Hat out already.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.88,0:22:08.97,Main,Mouse,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:10.78,Main,Mice,0,0,0,,Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:14.02,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Idiot, don't go out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:17.44,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,It seems being stripped of your shadow won't kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:19.31,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,It didn't kill Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.31,0:22:21.36,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,We can't go out yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.36,0:22:22.32,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,We'll wait for our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.77,0:22:24.69,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,It seems like they're going to do something with Luffy's shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.69,0:22:29.49,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,We need to see what happens to it so we can get it back later!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.49,0:22:32.20,Main,Zombie General,0,0,0,,Those two are no longer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:33.53,Main,Zombie General,0,0,0,,Where did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.51,0:22:37.36,Main,Zombie General,0,0,0,,I can't believe they got Tararan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.36,0:22:38.90,Main,Gigoro,0,0,0,,Where's the enemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.90,0:22:40.54,Main,Gigoro,0,0,0,,I'll cut them in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.49,0:22:47.21,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Franky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.21,0:22:50.55,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,What do you want?! I'm not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:54.06,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Idiot, don't look this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.06,0:22:57.52,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Why did you ask him... such a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:00.91,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Shut up! Don't mind me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.70,0:23:06.44,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Dammit! I love that skeleton now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:08.74,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,There isn't a guy that good anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.74,0:23:10.58,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.14,0:23:14.01,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.87,0:23:26.25,Main,Ryuuma,0,0,0,,As I thought, you're not gonna give up by merely kicking you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.25,0:23:27.63,Main,Brooke,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.28,0:23:31.05,Main,Ryuuma,0,0,0,,Don't you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.05,0:23:34.45,Main,Ryuuma,0,0,0,,Anyone who hears the name Swordmaster Ryuuma will cower in fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.45,0:23:35.44,Main,Brooke,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.44,0:23:36.72,Main,Brooke,0,0,0,,You're my shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.50,0:23:40.18,Main,Ryuuma,0,0,0,,There's a big difference between our bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.46,0:23:42.46,Main,Brooke,0,0,0,,You shall return...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.46,0:23:44.52,Main,Brooke,0,0,0,,To my feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.08,0:23:47.19,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.19,0:23:52.70,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Back when I saw his corpse in the Ice Country, I couldn't help but tremble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.70,0:23:59.48,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,It takes my breath away to think this repulsive thing rampaged through the seas 500 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.48,0:24:03.08,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,He took the entire island of each country he conquered to expand his own territory...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.32,0:24:01.77,Secondary,Hogback,0,0,0,,Cold...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.08,0:24:06.63,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,And thus he built the so called Evil Country.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.63,0:24:11.07,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,The very founder of the Country-Puller legend is right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.07,0:24:13.01,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,This will be the best zombie ever create-!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.01,0:24:16.78,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,The legend will be reborn once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.25,0:24:25.05,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Now... it's time to resurrect...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.05,0:24:27.44,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,The only man in history...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.40,0:24:31.99,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,The wild warrior that was called the Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.91,0:24:36.41,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Oars!
